      "updated": 1757054433258,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Organization/Company: Open\nAI\nModel Name: GPT-4o\nModel Size: estimated\nnumber is 200B\nParameters, Open AI does\nnot share in public the\nexact number\nContext Length: The model\naccepts 128K tokens which\nis around K 512K\ncharacters\nPrecision: estimated BF16\n(16-bit precision)\nGPT-4o is trained on much\nmore parameters ( around\n27 times more parameters\n) than Mistral, also\naccepts more tokens by 4\ntimes so this difference in\nspecs explains the\ndifference and quality of\nthe results.",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 18,
      "containerId": "dEv77UwE2UiFcHhIIrUjK",
      "originalText": "Organization/Company: Open AI\nModel Name: GPT-4o\nModel Size: estimated number is 200B Parameters, Open AI does not share in public the exact number\nContext Length: The model accepts 128K tokens which is around K 512K characters\nPrecision: estimated BF16 (16-bit precision)\nGPT-4o is trained on much more parameters ( around 27 times more parameters ) than Mistral, also accepts more tokens by 4 times so this difference in specs explains the difference and quality of the results.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aj",
      "frameId": null,
      "autoResize": true
    },
