      "text": "Organization/Company:\nMistral AI (French Company)\nModel Name: Mistral-7B-\nInstruct-v0.3\nModel Size: 7.25B\nParameters\nContext Length: The model\naccepts 32K tokens which\nis around 96K - 128K\ncharacters\nPrecision: BF16 (16-bit\nprecision)",
